755
00:47:47,220 --> 00:47:50,940
but you still came forward to take in a stranger's child.

756
00:47:50,940 --> 00:47:54,580
I thought you were so innocent.

757
00:47:57,210 --> 00:47:59,890
You say such silly things.

758
00:47:59,890 --> 00:48:03,920
Not at all. I'm really thankful to you.

759
00:48:03,920 --> 00:48:07,900
Hae Joon received everything in this house

760
00:48:07,900 --> 00:48:10,250
that my sister and I couldn't provide.

761
00:48:10,250 --> 00:48:13,820
So Hae Joon will be good to you.

762
00:48:13,820 --> 00:48:19,070
He's the type to give back tenfold once he grows up.

763
00:48:21,470 --> 00:48:23,180
Be good to me for what?

764
00:48:23,180 --> 00:48:25,600
There is no need.

765
00:48:25,600 --> 00:48:28,910
What parent asks his child for compensation for raising him?

766
00:48:39,720 --> 00:48:42,380
Is the galbi not good?

767
00:48:44,690 --> 00:48:47,230
- It's delicious. 
 - Oh, yes.

768
00:48:53,360 --> 00:48:55,200
Oh my, that's refreshing.

769
00:48:55,200 --> 00:48:56,570
