779
00:49:55,430 --> 00:49:56,730
Yes.

780
00:49:58,320 --> 00:50:00,240
No, I'm fine.

781
00:50:00,240 --> 00:50:02,160
Let's go inside, Ahjusshi.

782
00:50:04,850 --> 00:50:06,950
No, but...

783
00:50:08,200 --> 00:50:13,310
