787
00:50:29,030 --> 00:50:33,560
Why must Hae Joon walk on eggshells?

788
00:50:33,560 --> 00:50:36,280
I wasn't saying he needed to walk on eggshells.

789
00:50:36,280 --> 00:50:38,570
It's because I'm so thankful.

790
00:50:38,570 --> 00:50:40,500
"Thankful..."

791
00:50:41,980 --> 00:50:47,010
