891
00:58:49,630 --> 00:58:53,400
We are still preparing. I'm sorry.

892
00:59:03,550 --> 00:59:05,270
You'll have to wait a little bit.

893
00:59:05,270 --> 00:59:07,690
If you're okay with that...

894
00:59:10,680 --> 00:59:12,970
You're Mr. Yoon Jeong Jae, right?

895
00:59:22,540 --> 00:59:24,650
Do you remember me?

